Pizza Algo

1. Decide which business to order from 
2. Decide what type of pizza to order
    2a. Select toppings
    2b. Select crust
3. Decide if you want to order online or call the store
4. Decide if you want delivery or carry out
5. Place your order with the chosen method
    5a. Decide to pay with cash
    5b. Decide to pay with card
6. Wait for pizza
    6a. If wrong order received, call the location.
    6b. If satisfied with order, leave a review.